					.dmpage-text
						p To provide houses with heat, a solid fuel boiler house is being built, utilizing wood chips.
						p TATNEFT has launched the reconstruction of two apartment buildings, where state-of-the-art energy-saving technologies and environmentally friendly materials will be applied. The construction is to be completed this fall.
						


						
